Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.03,0:24:26.78,TS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4\pos(156,543)\blur3.5\fs40\3c&H000000&\fnAdobe Garamond Pro}This story is a work of fiction. \NIt has absolutely no relation to any \Nreal persons, organizations, or events.
