Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.50,0:01:50.25,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's practice with just the mouthpiece for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.25,0:01:51.25,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.63,0:01:52.75,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there a problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.96,0:01:54.92,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.92,0:02:00.85,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just thinking that I want to be able to play music like you as soon as possible, Rio-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.85,0:02:02.76,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be rough.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.76,0:02:05.02,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes ma'am! Please guide me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.22,0:02:07.14,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll have breakfast now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.14,0:02:09.27,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,The dining room's that way. I'll head there first.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.27,0:02:10.45,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.70,0:02:21.12,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,It's rocky and rough.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.04,0:02:28.01,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be together from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.80,0:02:40.68,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.09,0:02:44.90,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,You suck!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.13,0:03:21.30,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,This was originally prepared to welcome you last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.30,0:03:23.68,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,A token of kindness from us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.68,0:03:25.35,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.89,0:03:30.39,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, Rio, did you take the fish I was drying upstairs?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.39,0:03:33.27,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.27,0:03:34.78,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,That's weird...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.40,0:03:38.73,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Noel.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.73,0:03:40.86,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to sleep, do it after breakfast.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.03,0:03:44.21,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll try...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.83,0:03:48.79,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you just say you'd try?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.79,0:03:50.50,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm trying...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.62,0:03:56.59,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Rio-senpai's...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.59,0:04:01.88,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up. The food's getting cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.56,0:04:15.73,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, let me formally introduce you to the members of Platoon 1121.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.73,0:04:17.95,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,First would be the commanding officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.86,0:04:22.99,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Second Lieutenant Felicia Heideman,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.99,0:04:24.53,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,the tank commander.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.53,0:04:26.28,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's have a good time together.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.66,0:04:28.74,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.49,0:04:31.21,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Over here is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.58,0:04:35.01,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Noel...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.63,0:04:39.55,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Kannagi Noel...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.85,0:04:53.43,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,She's Corporal Kannagi, the pilot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.43,0:04:55.65,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,She's in charge of the maintenance as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.52,0:04:57.90,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Pleased to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.69,0:05:02.87,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,And finally...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.86,0:05:07.53,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Private Suminoya Kureha,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.53,0:05:08.92,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,the gunner.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.91,0:05:11.62,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen here,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.62,0:05:15.50,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I may be younger, but I've been serving longer than you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.50,0:05:17.76,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,So you'd better do as I sa{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.17,0:05:24.22,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,She overworked herself, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.22,0:05:26.77,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the hard work, Noel-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.93,0:05:33.32,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, let's start eating.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.48,0:05:35.44,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.65,0:05:39.40,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.73,0:05:43.90,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, help yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.90,0:05:45.83,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the food!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.95,0:05:50.66,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,This is happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.08,0:05:53.24,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,The bacon's hand-made,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.24,0:05:54.66,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,so eat a lot, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.66,0:05:55.62,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.62,0:05:58.54,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Stamina is important to both soldier and trumpeter.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.54,0:06:00.71,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,So eat well and grow your body.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.30,0:06:10.10,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.93,0:06:16.15,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Kureha.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.02,0:06:18.39,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.39,0:06:22.28,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Give her a tour of the base after breakfast.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.32,0:06:27.53,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger that...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.82,0:06:32.74,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Atten-tion!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.49,0:06:38.46,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm {\i1}really{\i0} busy right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.46,0:06:42.38,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,but since it's an order, I'll {\i1}have{\i0} to show you around.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.38,0:06:43.54,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.54,0:06:46.05,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for your time, Kureha-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.05,0:06:48.88,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't act familiar with me, Private Sorami!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.88,0:06:50.76,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry! Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.18,0:06:53.65,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Private Suminoya-dono!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.35,0:06:58.18,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.18,0:07:00.56,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's begin. Before the platoon and national flag...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.35,0:07:02.78,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Salute!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.36,0:07:10.11,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Our Tank Platoon 1121 currently consists of five people.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.11,0:07:16.62,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,They are: one Second Lieutenant, one Sergeant Major, one Corporal and two Privates.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.62,0:07:18.41,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,That's five.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.41,0:07:21.08,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Private Suminoya-dono!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.08,0:07:25.46,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the bare minimum for a unit, so basically...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.46,0:07:29.72,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,You could say we're elites.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.72,0:07:30.97,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.64,0:07:36.01,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Our unit deploys the following ordnance:
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.01,0:07:40.94,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,One tank, one heavy machine gun, two light machine guns,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.94,0:07:43.99,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,four rifles, and... five handguns...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.77,0:07:50.11,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Maintaining the national border of Trois, Seize with these ordnance,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.11,0:07:51.86,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,is our mission!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.86,0:07:52.83,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.87,0:07:58.71,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,P-Private Suminoya-dono, I have a question!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.54,0:08:01.75,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.75,0:08:04.54,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Permission granted, Private Sorami.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.54,0:08:06.34,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.25,0:08:10.84,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, if I remember correctly, beyond the borders of Seize is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.34,0:08:15.06,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed, beyond those mountains is No Man's Land.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.39,0:08:19.85,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,But, our Helvetia Republic extends to this point.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.85,0:08:22.06,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is a border fort! The front line!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.06,0:08:24.19,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an important base!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.19,0:08:29.07,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore, guard duty is critical. We perform the night watch in five shifts.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.07,0:08:31.08,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Sleeping on duty is forbidden.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.74,0:08:36.62,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,And this is the one and only hotline in this town that connects to the government center.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.91,0:08:38.58,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.54,0:08:42.71,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,If it rings, it's important!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.71,0:08:47.79,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,So when it does, wake everyone up and we will enter high alert.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.79,0:08:48.63,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,You got that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.63,0:08:51.56,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Private Suminoya-dono!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.11,0:09:11.82,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,The CO's room and briefing room are on the second floor!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.82,0:09:13.79,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Unauthorized entry is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.28,0:09:17.36,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's allowed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.36,0:09:19.28,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,But be sure to knock before entering!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.53,0:09:21.37,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.37,0:09:25.04,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Heating the water and cleaning are done in turns.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.04,0:09:26.12,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,And also...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.12,0:09:29.51,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Bathing order is based on rank, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.59,0:09:35.55,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.59,0:09:39.72,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't taking a bath together much more fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.72,0:09:42.31,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain, what are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.31,0:09:43.47,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm cleaning the bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.47,0:09:45.77,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it Noel's turn today?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.77,0:09:48.11,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,But she seemed very tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.19,0:09:54.11,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not setting a good example as the commanding officer!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.11,0:09:55.69,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do it later.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.69,0:09:58.90,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Please act with dignity appropriate for a commanding officer!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.18,0:10:19.51,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.51,0:10:21.26,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Look closely.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.26,0:10:25.97,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the battle tank our Platoon 1121 deploys.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.97,0:10:29.69,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,The Vector-Zero Automated Walker Tank, Takemikazuchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.69,0:10:32.02,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,It's much bigger than the one on the training grounds!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.53,0:10:38.03,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,That's because she's what people call a "zero-generation" tank.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.36,0:10:42.83,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,As a legacy of the old era, fewer than ten are left in this country.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.83,0:10:44.33,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.33,0:10:46.63,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,They say these were amazing tanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.45,0:10:49.63,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,But, the legs...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.71,0:10:53.67,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,It's still undergoing repairs since we're short on parts.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.13,0:10:59.17,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well yeah, there's not even a repair-manual,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.17,0:11:01.39,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,and parts are scarce as it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.39,0:11:05.43,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,But, Noel will do something about it, so it'll be okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.81,0:11:08.48,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm won't let you call it a mere decoration.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.89,0:11:12.20,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure she'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.77,0:11:14.07,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Someday...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.36,0:11:15.91,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.86,0:11:20.95,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't take us for fools.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.24,0:11:23.21,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,We slack off.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.12,0:11:27.20,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, our unit slacks off.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.20,0:11:30.91,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,We're even called "Seize's baggage" or "decorations" sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.91,0:11:34.46,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,We're part of the Pink Corps, yet we don't have a working tank.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.46,0:11:35.84,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.13,0:11:37.17,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Kureha-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.59,0:11:40.59,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,The tour ends here! Dismissed!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.51,0:11:45.65,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,They're getting along right away, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.89,0:11:47.05,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.35,0:11:50.60,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,They're just like us when we first met.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.81,0:11:53.28,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.60,0:11:56.69,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,There's only one thing that worries me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.69,0:12:00.11,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Last night, after you left to put Kana-chan to sleep...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.99,0:12:04.07,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain, why is she a signaller?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.32,0:12:09.04,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't reservists supposed to be either loaders or a pilots?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.04,0:12:13.34,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't help it. Heaquarters sent her to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.62,0:12:16.29,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Things don't always work out the way we want.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.29,0:12:16.88,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.25,0:12:20.80,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down, it'll be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.80,0:12:24.34,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Rio will look out for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.34,0:12:26.02,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like always.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.35,0:12:28.10,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, I'll do the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.93,0:12:37.20,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,She doesn't look like it, but she's perceptive. She might have guessed what's going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.56,0:12:39.20,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.23,0:12:42.62,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll have to do something about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.99,0:12:48.41,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,It showed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.66,0:12:50.91,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,What did?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.92,0:13:05.43,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,A ghost?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.80,0:13:07.39,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.10,0:13:14.77,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,That's just foolish.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.77,0:13:17.73,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,You must've been daydreaming like always.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.73,0:13:18.77,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought so.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.77,0:13:20.61,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, "thought so"?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.61,0:13:22.44,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw a ghost, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.57,0:13:25.70,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,At the barracks, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.20,0:13:27.20,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.86,0:13:30.74,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what are you saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.74,0:13:33.20,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,But, aren't ghosts common?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.20,0:13:36.42,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you to stop saying that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.42,0:13:38.67,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Noel, you're not any better.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.67,0:13:42.96,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,As an engineer, you should report after properly and scientifically investigating it yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.96,0:13:43.46,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.42,0:13:45.47,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.72,0:13:46.72,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,It's scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.72,0:13:48.39,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.39,0:13:50.14,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no such thing as ghosts!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.14,0:13:52.72,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,There's none! There's none! I refuse to believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.06,0:14:03.40,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I agree with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.40,0:14:04.53,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.53,0:14:05.40,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.40,0:14:06.53,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Ghosts don't exist!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.53,0:14:07.28,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,They don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.28,0:14:08.36,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,They absolutely don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.36,0:14:09.66,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,It's absolutely absolute!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.66,0:14:10.46,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.29,0:14:14.74,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Investigate the perimeter thoroughly!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.54,0:14:18.25,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Just blow your trumpet if you encounter the enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.25,0:14:20.42,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll send reinforcements right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.42,0:14:22.30,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.13,0:14:27.76,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, Private-dono.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.76,0:14:30.89,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want, Kana{\fscx300}-{\fscx100} Private!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.89,0:14:34.52,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a little... exciting, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.94,0:14:42.06,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,The thunder sounds like a marching drum.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.06,0:14:43.19,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a mission!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.19,0:14:44.86,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,We're not here to play around.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.86,0:14:47.69,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up, Kana{\fscx300}-{\fscx100} Private Sorami.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.69,0:14:49.91,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,You take point, I'll cover you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.91,0:14:50.70,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.70,0:14:52.42,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, move out!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.42,0:15:10.55,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,They say this wing remains as it was before this building became a fortress.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.88,0:15:13.55,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,What was it used for before?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.55,0:15:16.06,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,How would I know?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.06,0:15:17.77,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Just go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.77,0:15:18.56,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.25,0:15:45.79,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Ideographs.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.79,0:15:47.21,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what's written in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.21,0:15:50.80,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't just randomly look at stuff you can't even read.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.80,0:15:53.09,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,It would be great if I could read it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.09,0:15:56.35,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just some silly nonsense from long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.35,0:15:58.11,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's keep moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.27,0:16:05.94,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.94,0:16:06.61,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.11,0:16:09.48,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,You're dense.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.48,0:16:13.82,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,But, aren't ghosts supposed to protect us?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.82,0:16:14.82,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.82,0:16:21.12,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, in my hometown, we held an annual festival to thank the ghosts.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.12,0:16:22.87,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of backwater place is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.87,0:16:24.67,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,What you call a "ghost",
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.67,0:16:28.96,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,is something that possesses people, sucks blood, moves corpses,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.96,0:16:31.76,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,and does all sorts of bad things.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.44,0:16:46.86,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,That was a close call.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.86,0:16:50.58,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,They say rats carry all sorts of disease...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.36,0:16:53.57,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,What? So you do get scared after{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.29,0:17:05.62,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Are they gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.62,0:17:07.09,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.30,0:17:15.84,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kureha.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.84,0:17:17.09,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Private-dono.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.02,0:17:27.35,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I was thinking, this place could have been a school.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.86,0:17:34.69,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no school building this big, even in the government center.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.69,0:17:38.87,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,But, long ago there were more people, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.87,0:17:44.58,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,So back then, there must have been lots of kids our age gathering in this building,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.58,0:17:46.88,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,studying together.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.46,0:17:50.46,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,What, what? What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.46,0:17:52.46,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,They must have studied music in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.09,0:17:55.52,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Without being in the military?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.05,0:17:57.73,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Just look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.14,0:18:01.47,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.56,0:18:05.85,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I can't read it {\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.85,0:18:12.32,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,D-sharp.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.32,0:18:13.61,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx300}-{\fscx100} these notes...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.94,0:18:15.62,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,...never change.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.42,0:18:37.59,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you getting lost in thought for?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.59,0:18:38.56,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Now what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.18,0:18:41.34,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kureha-chan, isn't it lovely?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.34,0:18:42.18,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,What is?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.18,0:18:43.10,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.10,0:18:44.60,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.10,0:18:49.14,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,This town of Seize, this fortress,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.14,0:18:51.27,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,and everyone in this unit!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.61,0:19:00.20,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,We're just a small and insignificant unit in the countryside.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.07,0:19:07.12,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,The tank isn't working, and they often forget to resupply us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.12,0:19:10.25,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,We're assigned useless missions.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.25,0:19:12.13,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,We always slack off.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.00,0:19:14.76,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,But you love it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.30,0:19:23.89,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! Stay away!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.89,0:19:25.22,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,What, what? What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.14,0:19:28.48,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,It appeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.48,0:19:31.36,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Wait for me, Kureha!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.65,0:19:36.82,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.29,0:19:49.58,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.58,0:19:51.12,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.33,0:19:59.56,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the gunner of this very wonderful Platoon 1121 that I love so much, after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.64,0:20:08.93,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is the true form of the ghost, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.56,0:20:12.32,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,What's so ghostly about it anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.36,0:20:20.12,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you. You look {\i1}exactly{\i0} like yesterday's thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.40,0:20:24.24,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll put you on a spit!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.57,0:20:28.37,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't scare an injured animal like that, Rio.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.37,0:20:29.58,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.58,0:20:33.75,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,It must've had nowhere else to go, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.79,0:20:37.79,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, why don't you tell me what our unit's symbol is.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.92,0:20:42.51,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,We'd be punished if we tried to barbecue it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.80,0:20:45.09,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Shuko-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.09,0:20:47.01,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,It has a name already?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.30,0:20:49.89,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,But, I think this is wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.89,0:20:53.56,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,You almost died yesterday because of this thing, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.56,0:20:57.28,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,But, thanks to it, I had a great adventure today.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.44,0:20:59.77,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Kureha-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.77,0:21:01.65,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.65,0:21:05.03,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,That doesn't even qualify as an adventure!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.66,0:21:09.53,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,My, my. I guess this is majority rule, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.53,0:21:13.08,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's a commanding officer's order.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.08,0:21:16.54,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,But the next time you steal food, I'll punish you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.25,0:21:18.89,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.13,0:22:04.26,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,You did the morning call today, Rio?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.26,0:22:08.38,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,If Kanata were to do it every day, we'd get complaints from the townspeople.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.38,0:22:09.64,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.77,0:22:17.64,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,That's your seat, Kana-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.73,0:22:25.41,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Kureha-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.65,0:22:29.49,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I just happened to find a matching chair.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.49,0:22:31.41,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like I did it for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.58,0:22:33.91,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.50,0:22:38.46,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, stop it! Jeez!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.25,0:22:38.46,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.46,0:22:40.09,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,That's dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.29,0:22:43.71,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.71,0:22:45.14,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,The food...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.97,0:24:20.02,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode: The Squad`s Day: Rio Runs
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.90,0:00:18.28,OP-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2.2\fad(130,130)}The radiance of this sky will carry to your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.87,0:00:28.59,OP-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2.2\fad(130,130)}The melody you dreamed of is like serenity
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.59,0:00:33.59,OP-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2.2\fad(130,130)}For your hands the dream is still far away, but
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.59,0:00:38.60,OP-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2.2\fad(130,130)}remember the voice so gentle
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.60,0:00:51.32,OP-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2.2\fad(130,130)}That someone sung for you is happiness
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.32,0:01:00.74,OP-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2.2\fad(130,130)}The sound of the skies echoes high over all sadness
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.74,0:01:11.38,OP-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2.2\fad(130,130)}Everything reflected in your eyes is the real world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.38,0:01:20.97,OP-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2.2\fad(130,130)}Even if you shed tears, you cannot stop here
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.97,0:01:33.28,OP-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2.2\fad(130,130)}We're seperated a long way from tomorrow in the lights that rain without end
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.46,0:22:51.26,ED-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}Pile up the feelings of love and friendship
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.26,0:22:54.35,ED-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}Performing is also important
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.74,0:23:12.36,ED-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}I cried happily
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.49,0:23:18.29,ED-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}I laughed eagerly
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.75,0:23:27.59,ED-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}But all of them make me alive
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.59,0:23:31.76,ED-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}Let's walk slowly
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.76,0:23:33.59,ED-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}Everybody singing
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.59,0:23:37.68,ED-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}Tell me why we dance
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.68,0:23:38.97,ED-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}you just my friend
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.97,0:23:45.11,ED-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}Even if love and friendship change over time
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.11,0:23:50.57,ED-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}I want them to echo forever
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.11,0:23:56.91,ED-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}Speaking endless words touched by love
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.91,0:24:03.04,ED-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}Our harmony
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.08,0:24:07.67,ED-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}I can hear our harmony
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.89,0:24:21.89,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,
